Wins awarded for left to right adjacent symbol combinations of any size.

The TUMBLE FEATURE means that after every spin, winning combinations are paid and all winning symbols disappear. The remaining symbols fall to the bottom of the screen and the empty positions are replaced with new symbols coming from above. New symbols are of the same size as the initial spin result, before tumbles.
Tumbling will continue until no more winning combinations appear as a result of a tumble.
All wins are added to the player's balance after all the tumbles resulted from a base spin have been played.
Special reels are in play during FREE SPINS feature.
The player has the option to select the bet multiplier. Depending on the selected bet, the game behaves differently. The possible values are:
High volatility games pay out less often on average but the chance to hit big wins in a short time span is higher.
Only the highest win is paid per winning combination on the same pay way.
When winning on multiple pay ways, all wins are added to the total win.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
Free spins win is awarded to the player after the round completes.
Free spins total win in the history contains the whole win of the cycle.
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.

During the free spins round WILD symbols hit with a random multiplier of 2x, 3x or 5x. Every time a WILD is involved in a winning combination it's multiplier is accumulated in a tumble multiplier indicator. All WILD multipliers that hit during a tumble sequence multiply between each other. At the end of the tumble sequence the accumulated multiplier applies to the total win of that tumble sequence.
Hit 3 or more BONUS symbols during the feature to win 5 more free spins.

BRKOS PAPILDSPLES laik pc katra grieziena tiek izmaksti laimesti par laimjom kombincijm, bet visi laimjoie simboli pazd. Atlikuie simboli krt uz leju, bet tuks vietas ieem no augas krtoie simboli. Jaunajiem simboliem ir tds pats izmrs k simboliem pirms sabrukanas.
Spou brukana turpinsies, kamr vairs nebs laimgo kombinciju.
Visi laimesti tiek ieskaitti spltja kont pc tam, kad pirm grieziena izraist brukana ir beigusies.
BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU funkcijas laik splana notiek uz pam spolm.
Spltjam ir iespja izvlties likmes reizintju. Sples noteikumi mains atkarb no izvlts likmes. Iespjamie reizintji ir:
Augstas neparedzambas sples vidji izmaks laimestus retk, tau iespja gt lielus laimestus s laika sprd ir augstka.
Tiek izmaksts tikai augstkais laimests par laimesta kombinciju vien izmaksas ce.
Ja laimjat vairkos izmaksas ceos, visi laimesti tiek pievienoti kopjam laimestam.
Visas vrtbas ir izteiktas k aktulie laimesti monts.
Bezmaksas griezieni tiek pieirti spltjam pc raunda beigm.
Bezmaksas griezienu laimestu vstur tiek iekauta visa cikla kopj laimesta summa.
Darbbas traucjumi anul visas izmaksas un sples.

Bezmaksas griezienu raunda laik WILD simboli tiek uzgriezti ar nejauu reizintju 2x, 3x vai 5x apmr. Katru reizi, kad tiek uzgriezts WILD simbols, t reizintjs tiek pieskaitts pie brukanas reizintja. Visi WILD reizintji, kas tiek uzgriezti brukanas laik, tiek reizinti sav starp. Brukanas beigas uzkrtais reizintjs tiek piemrots kopjam brukanas laimestam.
Raunda laik uzgriez 3 vai vairk BONUS simbolus, lai iegtu 5 vai vairk bezmaksas griezienus.
Prkot BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENU papildspli, tiek nejaui uzgriezti 4, 5 vai 6 BONUS simboli, kas nejaui pieir 12, 17 vai 22 bezmaksas griezienus.
WILD simbols pards tikai uz 2., 3., 4. un 5. spoles.

Likmes reizintjs 25x - iespja laimt BEZMAKSAS GRIEZIENUS ir dubultota, uz spolm ir vairk BONUS simbolu, bet simbolu laimestu tabula paliek bez izmaim un laimests par tiem tiek izmaksts k 20x likmes reizintjs.
